org.gephi.datalab.plugin.manipulators.columns.merge

Class CreateTimeInterval

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gephi.datalab.plugin.manipulators.columns.merge.CreateTimeInterval
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AttributeColumnsMergeStrategy, Manipulator

    public class CreateTimeInterval
extends Object
implements AttributeColumnsMergeStrategy
    AttributeColumnsMergeStrategy for 1 or 2 columns that uses the column values as dates or numbers for start/end times to create or fill the TimeInterval column for each row.
    Author:
    Eduardo Ramos
